<p>*In-person&nbsp;<a href="https://www.elections.il.gov/VotingAndRegistrationSystems/EarlyVotingLocationsSearch.aspx" rel=" noopener" target="_blank">"Grace Period" registration is available in Illinois.</a> Grace period registration extends the voter registration deadline from the 27th day prior to an election through Election Day.&nbsp;</p>

<p><em>Updated on November 8, 2024.</em></p>

